origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.get_family_info",
        "description": "获取家庭成员的基本信息，包括年龄、职业、健康状况等。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "family_info",
                "description": "包含家庭成员信息的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.get_product_details",
        "description": "根据产品名称获取保险产品的详细信息，包括保障范围、保费、理赔流程等。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "product_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险产品的名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "product_details",
                "description": "包含保险产品详细信息的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.provide_selection_advice",
        "description": "根据家庭成员信息和产品详情，提供保险产品选择的建议。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "family_info",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "家庭成员信息的JSON对象。"
            },
            {
                "name": "product_details",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "保险产品详细信息的JSON对象。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "selection_advice",
                "description": "包含保险产品选择建议的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.recommend_products",
        "description": "根据家庭成员信息推荐适合的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "family_info",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "家庭成员信息的JSON对象。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "insurance_products",
                "description": "包含推荐保险产品列表的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.compare_products",
        "description": "比较多个保险产品的优劣，帮助用户做出决策。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "product_list",
                "type": "ARRAY",
                "description": "需要比较的保险产品列表。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison_result",
                "description": "包含产品比较结果的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.calculate_premium",
        "description": "根据家庭成员信息和选择的保险产品，计算每年的保费。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "family_info",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "家庭成员信息的JSON对象。"
            },
            {
                "name": "product_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "选择的保险产品名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "annual_premium",
                "description": "每年的保费金额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FamilyInsurance.check_eligibility",
        "description": "检查家庭成员是否符合特定保险产品的投保条件。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "family_info",
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "description": "家庭成员信息的JSON对象。"
            },
            {
                "name": "product_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险产品名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "eligibility_status",
                "description": "包含投保资格状态的JSON对象。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
